oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of the 90th Aero Squadron, Lebourne, France
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photograph of the 90th Aero Squadron was taken in Lebourne, France and belonged to Cpl. John Shannon Garrett, an electrician in the squadron. Garrett worked in the 90th Aero Squadron repairing, installing, and maintaining the radios in the planes and the radio station. He also served for a time in the 70th Aero Squadron.
